Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=============OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:33.72,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:40.31,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:47.28,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久 我一直将你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:51.45,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:58.58,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来将自己身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:05.17,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作是临时的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.76,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着 逃避着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.68,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃向梦想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:16.93,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.89,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.81,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与想象中相反的单纯内里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.77,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让那稚嫩的自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:29.74,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵阵刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:38.20,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 拖着泥泞沉重的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:43.46,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少身体强悍 所以今天也微笑面对吧
